<div style="padding:0px 20px 0px 10px;">
  <div class="title">Computer Consultant (Houston, TX)</div>
<p><b>JOB DESCRIPTION</b></p>
<p> <br />
We are looking for a friendly Computer Consultant for 
our small and growing company which supports small businesses and home 
computer users in the greater Houston area. If you are passionate about 
helping people with their computers, like traveling around the city 
to customer sites and working out of your home, then this is the position 
for you. If you have worked in a corporate environment and would like 
a change to a smaller organization where your strengths are acknowledged 
and you are celebrated, we would love to talk with you. Must be a team 
player.  Gray hair welcomed. </p>
<p> <br />
Typical jobs you will perform: </p>
<ul type="DISC">
  <li><b>Hardware -</b> 
  Installation, troubleshooting and repair of PCs, Macs, servers, networks, 
  printers, tablets, and smartphones.  </li>
  <li><b>Software -</b> 
  Installation and troubleshooting of Windows, MacOS, iOS, Android, Office 
  and other software, virtual Exchange Servers, e-mail and backup systems.  
  Also virus/spyware removal, general cleanup and computer optimization. </li>
  <li><b>Networking</b> 
  - Installation and troubleshooting of wired and wireless networking 
  including routers, switches and repeaters.  </li>
  <li><b>Training</b> 
  - One-on-one training on hardware, software, or networking at customer 
  request.</li>
</ul>
<p> <br />
<b>JOB LOCATION <br />
</b></p>
<p>Our office is in the 610 and 
290 area; however, you will be based from home. We will set up your 
home computer and your smartphone to login to the CRM system and get 
your daily schedule.  <br />
 <br />
<b>JOB REQUIREMENTS</b> <br /></p>
<ul type="DISC">
  <li>Must be personable 
  and communicate well with customers</li>
  <li>Have over 2 years 
  of relevant computer support experience</li>
  <li>Microsoft and/or 
  CompTIA certifications or equivalent</li>
  <li>Mac experience a 
  plus</li>
  <li>Pass a background 
  check</li>
  <li>Must have a reliable 
  car</li>
  <li>Nonsmoker <br />
  </li>
</ul>
<p><b>PAY AND 
BENEFITS</b> <br /></p>
<ul type="DISC">
  <li>Hourly + commission. 
  Range is $30,000 -$40,000 per year</li>
  <li>IRA contribution</li>
  <li>Cell phone allowance</li>
  <li>Mileage</li>
  <li>Training and certification 
  reimbursement.</li>
</ul>
 <br />
<p><b>APPLY FOR THIS JOB</b> <br />
</p>
<p>Please send your resume and a cover letter describing why you would like this 
job to <a style="color: #000000;" href="mailto:&#100;&#099;&#108;&#101;&#114;&#099;&#064;&#099;&#108;&#101;&#114;&#099;&#046;&#099;&#111;&#109;"><strong>
                    &#100;&#099;&#108;&#101;&#114;&#099;&#064;&#099;&#108;&#101;&#114;&#099;&#046;&#099;&#111;&#109;</strong></a>. Only resumes <b>WITH</b> proper cover letters are considered. </p>
